";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1046965\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:385:\"On 17-19 May 2019, WordCamp Bristol took place at the University of Chemistry. A well-attended event that represented the South West of England&#8217;s WordPressers as well as the many UK and international users, coders, developers, sponsors, and contributors. About Bristol WordCamp 2019 After two years, we finally got to enjoy another brilliantly organised WordCamp. Okay, [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Ronald\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19291:\"<p>On 17-19 May 2019, WordCamp Bristol took place at the University of Chemistry. A well-attended event that represented the South West of England&#8217;s WordPressers as well as the many UK and international users, coders, developers, sponsors, and contributors.</p>\n<h2>About Bristol WordCamp 2019</h2>\n<p>After two years, we finally got to enjoy another brilliantly organised WordCamp. Okay, I might be a little bit biased here as I was one of the 9 organisers and coordinated the volunteers. But as always it takes a whole group of dedicated volunteers to put up a show. This time the number of attendees had grown to almost double, which meant a new location to accommodate this fantastic community. This is not an exaggeration as the vibe, inclusion, and accessibility meant that everyone felt welcome. There was also a big emphasis on creating a low carbon footprint and &#8216;being green&#8217;. I think few people would disagree that being conscious of these factors is a bad thing.</p>\n<h3>Day 1- the contributor day</h3>\n<p>The contributor day took place right by the water called The Pavilion, No1 Hannover Quay. Various contributions were made to WordPress from theme reviews to support and WordPress TV. However, I wonder how you could stay focused in such a lovely location and view. In the evening this was transformed to the social venue and to thank all the sponsors, volunteers, speakers and organisers.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047745\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047745\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047745 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047745\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Contributor day</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047738\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047738\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047738 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047738\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Volunteers ready to welcome attendees</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047741\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047741\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047741 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047741\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The YITH stand &#8211; ready to hand out swag</figcaption></figure>\n<h3>Day 2 &#8211; Conference day and after party</h3>\n<p>An early start for as I needed to set up the sponsorship table before the attendees would embark onto the University of Bristol&#8217;s Chemistry department. The location and venue was a big part of the success of this year&#8217;s WordCamp. Two lecture rooms, a quiet room and a huge space for all attendees to mingle with sponsors while drinking coffee or having lunch. It is usually the case that the first part of the day just flies by. Many WordPressers love a bit of swag and our #KeepCalmAndClearCache t-shirts did not disappoint the Bristol crowd. What was lovely to hear was that so many of those who came to see me are users of our plugins. This is one of the main reasons why we attend so many WordPress events, to meet you&#8230; It is also a great opportunity to hear feedback, discuss new launches and get ideas by talking to users.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047748\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047748\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047748 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047748\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lots of interest from the attendees</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047744\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047744\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047744 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047744\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Vegetarian lunchtime buffet</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047737\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047737\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047737 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"people socializing\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047737\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Evening social at the Watershed</figcaption></figure>\n<p>The evening social took place at the Watershed. You get the chance to catch up with old and new friends whilst reflecting on all the new things you&#8217;ve learned that day. &#8216;Make your own burritos&#8217; is a great way to feed a large group with various dietary requirements. The atmosphere was a bit too good to not finish the evening in various other bars down by the quay.</p>\n<h3>Day 3 &#8211; Conference day</h3>\n<p>Another fine and quiet morning marching up the hill for a slightly later start than the day before&#8230; For those that attended WordCamp Bristol, you probably regretted not getting a hotel higher up the hill as it was most certainly a steep one. As usual, the catering was set up and coffee and biscuits were welcoming the WordPressers that would attend day two. A whole day of 2 tracks with speakers lined up kept everyone wondering which talk to attend till the last moment. Often to make mental notes to catch up on the &#8216;other&#8217; talk on WordPress TV. As most YITH plugin users probably met up with Ronald on Saturday, it was more obvious that on Sunday it was the turn of WordPressers that wanted to find out more. This is just as important to us, as WordCamps are a great way to introduce new users to the extended world of WooCommerce.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047735\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047735\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047735 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"keepcalmandclearcache t-shirt\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047735\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Happy attendee <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047740\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047740\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047740 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"holding t-shirts\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047740\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">More happy attendees <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047742\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047742\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047742 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047742\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Who wouldn&#8217;t be happy with cool swag <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f609.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></figcaption></figure>\n<h2>YITH as a gold sponsor of WordCamp Bristol</h2>\n<p>As a company, we felt honoured to be part of WordCamp Bristol and to be able to sponsor such a great and well-run event.</p>\n<p><strong>Thank you to each and every one of you</strong></p>\n<p>As much as I&#8217;d like to thank every person that made WordCamp Bristol possible, it would be an impossible task. Hannah and Janice, who were the leads, most certainly know how to put a super team together. They, in turn, the volunteers, speakers, venue, staff and every ticket holder they invited to join in one of the best WordCamp experiences of this year. It got me and the rest of YITH inspired and already looking forward to the next one.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047743\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047743\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047743 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"conference projector\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047743\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">WordCamp leads doing their Thank You&#8217;s</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047746\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047746\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047746 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"group of volunteers\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047746\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Thanks to all the volunteers and organisers</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047747\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047747\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047747 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"applause\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047747\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Attendees certainly showed their appreciation</figcaption></figure>\n<h3>WordPress Community and what it means for YITH</h3>\n<p>All of our staff contribute to the community in one way or another, whether it is by translating, coding or giving up time to teach the next generation about WordPress. While WordCamp Bristol was in full swing, two of our developers were at WordCamp Bari contributing, speaking and also sponsoring. You see, we love WordPress here at YITH!</p>\n<h3>Upcoming WordCamp events to meet us</h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047739\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047739\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047739 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"Ronald Gijsel\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047739\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Join Ronald from YITH at the next event</figcaption></figure>\n<p>The next WordCamp is most certainly going to be the biggest and the best. Yes, you guessed it&#8230; on 21 and 22 June, aver 3000 WordPress enthusiasts will embark on Berlin to listen, socialize, engage and get entertained by the WordPress Community. Many of the Bristol team will be there too and we will most certainly keep an eye out for them. Will you come to Berlin? Make sure you let us know on social media or during the event.</p>\n<p>Further on in the year, we will be in <a href=\"https://2019.brighton.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Brighton</a> (UK) <a href=\"https://2019.catania.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Catania</a> (It) and <a href=\"https://2019.nijmegen.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Nijmegen</a> (NL) with further WordCamps in the planning. If you&#8217;d like us to get involved in your WordPress community event, why not <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/contact/\">contact us</a> and we would consider supporting it.</p>\n<p>Looking forward to seeing you at the next community event!</p>\n<p>And finally, there is only one thing to remember&#8230;</p>\n<h4>#KeepCalmAndClearCache</h4>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>(photo credits: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Aleks_Creative\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Aleks</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/La_Lole\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Lorena</a>)</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:97:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/its-the-community-that-made-wordcamp-bristol-truly-amazing/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:122:\"WordPress lovers gathering again in Turin, this time under the viral slogan #keepcalmandclearcache – WordCamp Turin 2019\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:150:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordpress-lovers-gathering-again-in-turin-this-time-under-the-viral-slogan-keepcalmandclearcache-wordcamp-turin-2019/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:158:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordpress-lovers-gathering-again-in-turin-this-time-under-the-viral-slogan-keepcalmandclearcache-wordcamp-turin-2019/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 29 Apr 2019 14:13:02 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1035893\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:344:\"It’s an annual tradition now for us at YITH, we couldn’t miss the awesome event organized by the WordPress community in Turin: WordCamp Turin 2019! Hosted in the location of Toolbox Coworking, it started on April 5th with the Contributor Day. In the big room named “Keynote”, the attendees were crowding around the tables with [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"YITH Support Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6171:\"<p dir=\"ltr\">It’s an annual tradition now for us at YITH, we couldn’t miss the <strong>awesome event organized by the WordPress community in Turin</strong>: WordCamp Turin 2019!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hosted in the location of Toolbox Coworking, it started on April 5th with the Contributor Day.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In the big room named “Keynote”, the attendees were crowding around the tables with one common goal, contributing to WordPress for one whole day, be they developers, graphic designers, polyglots, marketers or mere WordPress lovers.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As soon as we arrived, after taking a cup of coffee, we sat down at <strong>WP Core table and worked on contributing to WordPress</strong> as well.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The location was perfect for the Contributor Day (as it was in the past years too) and everything was organised with great attention to the detail.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Saturday 6th April was the high point of the event: the conference day!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The first speeches began at 9:30 with topics ranging from development, content management, SEO, marketing, business and much more.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1037085\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2126\" height=\"785\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4.jpg 2126w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-300x111.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-768x284.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-1024x378.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-261x96.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-311x115.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-363x134.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-270x100.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2126px) 100vw, 2126px\" /></a></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Right from the start of the event and during the breaks, our t-shirts literally flew off the shelves!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The slogan printed on them <strong>“Keep calm and clear cache”</strong> won all people approaching the booth, they couldn’t help asking for one! Some of them use to collect all our t-shirts and could not absolutely miss this new piece.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1037086\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1672\" height=\"785\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2.jpg 1672w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-300x141.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-768x361.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-1024x481.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-261x123.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-311x146.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-363x170.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-270x127.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1672px) 100vw, 1672px\" /></a></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Among the many people that stopped to talk, to our great satisfaction, we could notice that most of them are using our products. As developers, it made us proud to hear statements like “I’ve been using your plugins for a while now, and I couldn’t do without them”.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1037087\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1672\" height=\"785\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1.jpg 1672w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-300x141.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-768x361.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-1024x481.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-261x123.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-311x146.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-363x170.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-270x127.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1672px) 100vw, 1672px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1037088\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2012\" height=\"735\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3.jpg 2012w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-300x110.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-768x281.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-1024x374.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-261x95.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-311x114.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-363x133.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-270x99.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2012px) 100vw, 2012px\" /></a></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">We also had the opportunity and pleasure to meet familiar faces and old friends. Not only could we hold business conversations with all of them, but also we spent a wonderful evening at the after party, held in the same location: board games, ping-pong, table football, karaoke… well, we did not miss anything!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>We want to thank both all the organisers and volunteers</strong> that worked hard to make the WordCamp result in such a successful and enjoyable event, and all the attendees who took part in the event: it couldn’t have been so great without them!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:155:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordpress-lovers-gathering-again-in-turin-this-time-under-the-viral-slogan-keepcalmandclearcache-wordcamp-turin-2019/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"Keep Calm and Clear your Cache – WordCamp London 2019\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/keep-calm-and-clear-your-cache-wordcamp-london-2019/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/keep-calm-and-clear-your-cache-wordcamp-london-2019/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 16 Apr 2019 15:37:07 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1034532\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:338:\"Keep Calm and Clear your Cache This was not just a WordCamp it was a WordCamp multiplied by three… London, Madrid and Turin all supporting #yithevents… But there was an added connection, which was the hashtag that linked us all &#8211; #keepcalmandclearcache. The t-shirts, with the motto printed on, that we gave to our new [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Ausilia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13334:\"<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Keep Calm and Clear your Cache</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This was not just a WordCamp it was a WordCamp multiplied by three… London, Madrid and Turin all supporting #yithevents… But there was an added connection, which was the hashtag that linked us all &#8211; #keepcalmandclearcache. The t-shirts, with the motto printed on, that we gave to our new and existing customers went down a storm.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1035235\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-2.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp London\" width=\"1000\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-2.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-2-363x290.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-2-300x240.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-2-768x614.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-2-261x209.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-2-311x249.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-2-270x216.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">I had the immense pleasure to represent YITH in London and it was my third time attending London WordCamp. Also, two years ago was the first time that I met up with Ausilia and Alberto. <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-london-a-great-experience-and-great-people/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-london-a-great-experience-and-great-people/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1554899737827000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHMf_nHW-vvEhdkFRCVjivWEfIIjA\">Read about it here &gt;</a> The event still has the same excitement and buzz as every year with this year’s theme around the London markets. It would also be the first time I was going to give a full-length talk at a WordCamp.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1035236\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1035236\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"wp-image-1035236 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-2.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp London\" width=\"1000\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-2.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-2-363x290.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-2-300x240.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-2-768x614.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-2-261x209.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-2-311x249.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-2-270x216.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1035236\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">London Metropolitan University building &#8211; Ronald at the YITH stand in the Grad Building &#8211; Opening remarks</figcaption></figure>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Day one &#8211; Saturday 6 April 2019</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">An early 6:30 start meant that I could take my time in setting up the YITH sponsor table in the graduate centre at the Metropolitan University. I was not the first to arrive, as the organisers were in full swing putting up posters and setting up the registration desk. What a commitment from the organising team, as I found out some were still setting up and testing the video streams at 1 am that morning! Coffee was my next thing to sort out at this time of the day. This year&#8217;s swag included a water bottle and a reusable insulated coffee cup. A really nice thing as everyone is much more conscious about the environment and sustainability.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The next three hours went by very quickly and before I realised I was surrounded by WordCamp attendees asking questions, collecting swag including the hottest item at the event, the ‘Keep Calm and Clear Cache’ t-shirt.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">I was pleasantly surprised by the number of existing customers coming over and simply saying: ‘I use a couple of your plugins and they are great and easy to use’. That is just so lovely to hear, but I do admit I was also enjoying the more challenging questions… like for example: ‘what should I use to have a <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-featured-audio-video-content/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-featured-audio-video-content/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1554899737827000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGEsSLWhWt3M9pvhKumj3TsjgTZ7g\">video playing in the gallery </a>of product images?’</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The day passed very quickly and I soon found myself in the ‘rocket’. This part of the building is were the bar and track A is located. With a couple of hours to spare, I met up with some old friends and chatted over a few beverages. The main conference room was changed over to accommodate the hundreds of attendees soon to enjoy a delicious filled baked potato with various types of chillies. After dinner, the beers were calling though I chose to get back to the hotel for a good night sleep as the next day would be a big one…</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1035978\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1035978\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"wp-image-1035978 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-bis.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"809\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-bis.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-bis-363x294.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-bis-300x243.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-bis-768x621.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-bis-261x211.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-bis-311x252.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-bis-270x218.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1035978\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ready to receive the hundreds of attendees &#8211; A busy Saturday morning at WordCamp London 2019 and our little helper Arda</figcaption></figure>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Day two &#8211; Sunday 7 April 2019</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Good Morning London! It was a nice and quiet early start but I had some revision to do. Before I tucked into a full English breakfast, I went over my talk, again. I love early mornings in a busy city as you see everyone setting up and travelling to start a new day of work or pleasure. My first priority was to get myself sorted in track B for my talk: ‘Are you ready to publish? The afterlife…’ I was talking about the value of blogs and news for small and medium businesses and that you should consider whether your efforts actually pay off. In the complex world of SEO, publishing, analytics and setting up goals, there is so much to consider. My main aim was to set off a spark to those that attended.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">I received amazing feedback from those in the room the ones outside, including from Team Yoast and even those who watched the live stream from the hotel room… it was Sunday morning after all.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">My helpers took charge of the YITH sponsor table and I was delighted to see a small crowd gathering around it again… While other talks were taking place I managed to finally chat to some of the other sponsors in my area. Team Yoast, A2 Hosting, Weglot, Jupiter X, WooCommerce, Jetpack, Bluehost and WP&amp;UP (a mental health charity dedicated to WordPress users) It is such a great community and we all supported each other over the two days whether it was to get some coffee or take turns going for lunch or just general feeling great being here and doing what we do.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1035238\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1035238\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"wp-image-1035238 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-2.jpg\" alt=\"Ready to receive the hundreds of attendees  - A busy Saturday morning at WordCamp London 2019\" width=\"1000\" height=\"454\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-2.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-2-363x165.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-2-300x136.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-2-768x349.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-2-261x118.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-2-311x141.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-2-270x123.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1035238\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ronald speaking at WordCamp London (photo credit: Elliott richmond) &#8211; Jupiter X with Maziar and Babek</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1035239\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1035239\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"wp-image-1035239 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-2.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp London 2019\" width=\"1000\" height=\"454\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-2.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-2-363x165.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-2-300x136.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-2-768x349.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-2-261x118.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-2-311x141.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-2-270x123.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1035239\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Siobhan and Jimmy from team Yoast &#8211; Ivan from Siteground and Ronald</figcaption></figure>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">The afterthoughts</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Organising a WordCamp is one of the most rewarding things to do but it really takes a lot of time and energy. I, myself am in the process of organising the second Bristol WordCamp and YITH will soon announce more details on a WordCamp in Catania. I want to thank each individual organiser, volunteer, university staff member, caterer for their efforts to make this a super exciting and smoothly run event. Dan Maby and Barbara Saul, in particular, deserve a special mention. They were the leads for this year’s WordCamp London and at the closing remarks, there was already talk about 2020…. I mean, what energy these two have and how truly inspiring to the rest of the WordPress community.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For YITH it has been very humbling too, to have taken part again in this event. But most importantly it is because of you, our supporters, users, club members that we love what we are doing. Thank you for coming over to see us and just one last thing… ‘Keep Calm and Clear your Cache’</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1035240\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1035240\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"wp-image-1035240 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/06-2.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp London 2019\" width=\"1000\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/06-2.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/06-2-363x133.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/06-2-300x110.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/06-2-768x282.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/06-2-261x96.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/06-2-311x114.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/06-2-270x99.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1035240\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dan Maby doing the closing remarks &#8211; YITH proudly sponsored this year’s WordCamp London</figcaption></figure>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Where to see us next?</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Our next WordCamps will be in:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">Bilbao &#8211; Spain &#8211; on the 27-28 April <a href=\"https://2019.bilbao.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://2019.bilbao.wordcamp.org/</a></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">Bari &#8211; Italy &#8211; on 17-18 May <a href=\"https://2019.bari.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://2019.bari.wordcamp.org/</a></li>\n<li>Bristol &#8211; United Kingdom &#8211; on the 17-19 May &#8211; <a href=\"https://2019.bristol.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://2019.bristol.wordcamp.org/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1554899737828000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFB8wPjTWNh9UfyVqDZ-M2HM3yuzg\">https://2019.bristol.wordcamp.<wbr />org/</a></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">Irùn &#8211; Spain &#8211; on the 1-2 June &#8211; <a href=\"https://2019.irun.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://2019.irun.wordcamp.org/</a></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">WORDCAMP EUROPE! Berlin &#8211; Germany &#8211; on the 20-22 June <a href=\"https://2019.europe.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://2019.europe.wordcamp.org/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Ronald Gijsel</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/keep-calm-and-clear-your-cache-wordcamp-london-2019/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"WordCamp Granada 2018 – Perfectly organised from A to Z\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-granada-2018-perfectly-organised-from-a-to-z/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-granada-2018-perfectly-organised-from-a-to-z/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 24 Dec 2018 13:54:02 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1007221\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:327:\"Granada´s very first WordCamp, and we were there! It got of to a great start on the contributor day, which was held in the University of Granada, where we had our first get- together and introduction to the upcoming event. Afterwards we took our chance to contribute to the WordPress community and joined the Support [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"YITH Support Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5714:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Granada´s very first WordCamp, and we were there! It got of to a great start on the contributor day, which was held in the University of Granada, where we had our first get- together and introduction to the upcoming event.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Afterwards we took our chance to contribute to the WordPress community and joined the Support and Polyglots tables to have a productive yet enjoyable afternoon!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>The venue was perfect for the contributor day</strong> and we could already tell that just like the first day, every part of the event was going to be organised well up until the smallest details.</span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1007222\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp Granada 2018\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-363x145.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-300x120.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-768x307.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-261x104.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-311x124.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-270x108.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the evening we were invited to the dinner for sponsors and speakers, which was in the famous neighbourhood of Albaicín, which makes you feel like you are walking around in a fairy tale or old movie with its narrow streets and amazing architecture and of course the <strong>Alhambra! Which</strong> we were very surprised to find out that the dinner had immediate views up on. </span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1007223\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp Granada 2018\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-363x145.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-300x120.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-768x307.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-261x104.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-311x124.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-270x108.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On the next day we found our ways to the Palacio de Congresos of Granada, <strong>where a great team of volunteers was ready to help us with whatever we needed</strong>, after a quick set-up we were ready for the doors to open!</span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1007224\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp Granada 2018\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-363x145.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-300x120.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-768x307.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-261x104.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-311x124.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-270x108.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We were all very heartwarmed by the song about code from Fran Torres.</span></p>\n<p><strong>And after the first talks started and during the networking and breaks our hilarious shirts went out very fast!</strong> Everyone loved them, probably because of the reletable phrase <strong>“It works on my PC”</strong> . Haven&#8217;t we all been there?!</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We saw many familiar faces but also had the chance to meet and have interesting chats with attendees from all around the world, from Spain to India!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The big smiles are not only thanks to the productive time spend listening and learning at the talks and workshops, I am sure this also had something to do with the provided lunch that included paella among various delicious treats! <strong>And the fact that the day was very well organised in this amazing location with a great turnout, in total almost 400 people!</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We would like to thank the organisation for setting up this spectacular weekend! And a big thumbs up to all volunteers, We appreciated all of your effort and care throughout the WordCamp and it would not have been possible without you! </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Both the event and city have made a great impression on us, and we will surely come back for a longer visit in the near future! </span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1007225\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp Granada 2018\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-363x145.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-300x120.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-768x307.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-261x104.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-311x124.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-270x108.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:92:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-granada-2018-perfectly-organised-from-a-to-z/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"WordPress 5.0 under the Christmas tree\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/wordpress-5-0-under-the-christmas-tree/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/wordpress-5-0-under-the-christmas-tree/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 05 Dec 2018 15:41:54 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"YITH News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1002420\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:313:\"Yesterday we have learned that WordPress 5.0 will be released on December 6th (tomorrow). This news was a surprise to us as we all thought it would have been released after the Christmas holidays. Given the short notice, we would like to give you some advice and make you consider a few things. We would [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Marco Salvo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2630:\"<p>Yesterday we have learned that WordPress 5.0 will be released on December 6th (tomorrow).</p>\n<p>This news was a surprise to us as we all thought it would have been released after the Christmas holidays.</p>\n<p>Given the short notice, we would like to give you some advice and make you consider a few things. We would also like to specify that YITH is ready for this new version.</p>\n<p>Before updating to WordPress 5.0, we want you to spend two minutes thinking about the future of your business and ask yourself some questions.</p>\n<h2>Do you think this is the right moment to update to WordPress 5.0?</h2>\n<p>December is a month when everyone is weighed down with work due to the upcoming holidays. All the stores are crowded and also online shops register this month as the most profitable of the year.</p>\n<p>Consider that in January, when holidays will be over, you can update calmly. Moreover, the patches already scheduled will be released and your system will be more stable.</p>\n<h2>Will your site work with Gutenberg?</h2>\n<p>WordPress 5.0 will integrate Gutenberg. Gutenberg is a new text editor with higher performances that will revolutionize the way of writing in WordPress. If you still don&#8217;t know about Gutenberg, I suggest referring to <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/gutenberg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">this</a>.</p>\n<p>YITH plugins are almost all ready and many have been already released with support to the new version, but since not all of them are ready, it is important for you to know whether those you are using can support the update.</p>\n<p>If you are using other plugins in addition to YITH ones that integrate with Gutenberg, please check (by testing them or consulting the plugin documentation) they are ready or at least that they won&#8217;t cause fatal errors. Otherwise, I suggest installing and activating the plugin <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/classic-editor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Classic Editor</a> before the update.</p>\n<p>Just to be clear, we love Gutenberg and YITH plugins have integrated blocks to use their own shortcodes. We are ready! Yet, we think this version will be even more stable and safer in January.</p>\n<p>Therefore, our advice is the following: <strong>slow and steady wins the race</strong>.</p>\n<h2>If you still want to update to WordPress 5.0</h2>\n<p>Before updating, make a backup. If you have a staging environment, we recommend testing there the new version first.</p>\n<p>If you don&#8217;t have any and your site is fully active and essential for your business, create one. This advice is valid also for any major release.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/wordpress-5-0-under-the-christmas-tree/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s: